Package: gsemr
Title: Genomic Structural Equation Modeling (Rust Backend)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Po-Hsuan", "Lai", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "pohsuanlai0208@gmail.com"),
    person("Andrew", "Grotzinger", role = "ctb", comment = "Original GenomicSEM R package")
  )
Description: A Rust-accelerated implementation of GenomicSEM for multivariate
    LD Score Regression and Structural Equation Modeling on GWAS summary
    statistics. Drop-in replacement for the R GenomicSEM package with
    identical results and significantly faster execution.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: Rust (>= 1.70), cargo
Imports: jsonlite
Suggests: bench, psych
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
